# HERD LP — NEVER commit real .env · NEVER paste keys in chat · NEVER screenshot
# If leaked: move funds out, delete .env, rotate the key.
# Use a fresh LP wallet. Fund it separately.
# On start the node may sell SOL toward the gas floor (~0.02) to buy ANSEM / seed pools.
#
# Canonical secrets file: .env (this file). Copy to .env and fill in.
# No quotes. Wrong: LP_WALLET_PUBLIC_KEY="AbC..."  Right: LP_WALLET_PUBLIC_KEY=AbC...
# Pubkey ~44 chars · private key ~88 chars base58 · password = any length you choose
LP_WALLET_PUBLIC_KEY=YOUR_LP_WALLET_PUBKEY_HERE
LP_PRIVATE_KEY=YOUR_LP_PRIVATE_KEY_BASE58_HERE
DASHBOARD_PASSWORD=CHANGE_ME

# —— $HERD launch (same CAs as hub NEXT_PUBLIC_HERD_*) ——
# Leave blank / XXXXXXXXXXXX until CA posts. Node runs TOKEN–ANSEM only until then.
# HERD_MINT=
# HERD_POOL=
# HERD_SYMBOL=HERD

# Optional fee destinations + split (Setup → Config sliders also write these)
# ANSEM_DEST_WALLET=
# FEE_SPLIT_ANSEM_SEND=0.05
# FEE_SPLIT_ANSEM_HOLD=0.05
# FEE_SPLIT_RESERVE=0.05
# FEE_SPLIT_REINVEST=0.85

# Optional RPC (public default works; paid endpoint if rate-limited)
# SOLANA_RPC_URL=
